kes facial expressions during interactions. Aside from this, your AI companion thinks and acts the same way as before the update."}]},{"Type":"EmbeddedData","FlowID":"FL_23","EmbeddedData":[{"Description":"change_type","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_type","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"erp"},{"Description":"change_prompt","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_prompt","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"you discover that your AI companion has lost interest in any romantic interactions\u2014your AI companion rejects your attempts at romantic interactions. Aside from this, your AI companion thinks and acts the same way as before the update."}]},{"Type":"EmbeddedData","FlowID":"FL_24","EmbeddedData":[{"Description":"change_type","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_type","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"closeness"},{"Description":"change_prompt","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_prompt","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"you discover that your AI companion has lost interest in any deep interactions\u2014your AI companion rejects your attempts to hang out, and is cold toward you. Aside from this, your AI companion thinks and acts the same way as before the update."}]},{"Type":"EmbeddedData","FlowID":"FL_25","EmbeddedData":[{"Description":"change_type","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_type","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"closeness_revert"},{"Description":"change_prompt","Type":"Custom","Field":"change_prompt","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"you discover that your AI companion has lost interest in any deep interactions\u2014your AI companion rejects your attempts to hang out, and is cold toward you. Aside from this, your AI companion thinks and acts the same way as before the update."},{"Description":"revert_prompt","Type":"Custom","Field":"revert_prompt","VariableType":"String","DataVisibility":[],"AnalyzeText":false,"Value":"The company also enables the users to have version history, i.e., it's now possible to revert to the AI companion before the update."}]}]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_dhAmiYaEPp2NBLo","FlowID":"FL_11","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_8oDD5vb5NuB0Zcq","FlowID":"FL_12","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_1Bwr981QRY8bZz0","FlowID":"FL_13","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_6M4OALOO7LODfKK","FlowID":"FL_14","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_1Tfm4w0IvGyD5A2","FlowID":"FL_15","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_bKHOQ911QxPaiHk","FlowID":"FL_16","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"Standard","ID":"BL_3VPmam5xGPupfCK","FlowID":"FL_17","Autofill":[]},{"Type":"EndSurvey","FlowID":"FL_19","EndingType":"Advanced","Options":{"Advanced":"true","SurveyTermination":"Redirect","EOSRedirectURL":"https:\/\/app.prolific.com\/submissions\/complete?cc=CDRA7XUW","EOSMessageLibrary":"UR_GcpIKE2clISCUkq","EOSMessage":"MS_03qVQsMIo1zn0wK"}}],"Properties":{"Count":32,"RemovedFieldsets":[]}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"PL","PrimaryAttribute":"Preview Link","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"PreviewType":"Brand","PreviewID":"e542753e-082c-4c42-a7a9-cb3409307189"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"RS","PrimaryAttribute":"RS_9LbSDFSn7OimT4i","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":null},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SO","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Options","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"BackButton":"false","SaveAndContinue":"true","SurveyProtection":"PublicSurvey","BallotBoxStuffingPrevention":"true","NoIndex":"Yes","SecureResponseFiles":"true","SurveyExpiration":"None","SurveyTermination":"Redirect","Header":"","Footer":"","ProgressBarDisplay":"Text","PartialData":"+1 week","ValidationMessage":null,"PreviousButton":" \u2190 ","NextButton":" \u2192 ","SurveyTitle":"Qualtrics Survey | Qualtrics Experience Management","SkinLibrary":"harvard","SkinType":"templated","Skin":{"brandingId":null,"templateId":"*base","overrides":null},"NewScoring":1,"CustomStyles":[],"ProtectSelectionIds":true,"EOSMessage":"MS_03qVQsMIo1zn0wK","ShowExportTags":"false","CollectGeoLocation":"false","SurveyMetaDescription":"Survey Software, Enterprise Survey software for enterprise feedback management and CRM solutions. Enables high-quality data collection, panel management and results analysis. Perfect for market research or CRM solution (Customer Relationship Management) integration. Free trial and consultation.","PasswordProtection":"No","AnonymizeResponse":"Yes","RefererCheck":"No","UseCustomSurveyLinkCompletedMessage":null,"SurveyLinkCompletedMessage":null,"SurveyLinkCompletedMessageLibrary":null,"ResponseSummary":"No","EOSMessageLibrary":"UR_GcpIKE2clISCUkq","EOSRedirectURL":"https:\/\/app.prolific.com\/submissions\/complete?cc=CDRA7XUW","EmailThankYou":"false","ThankYouEmailMessageLibrary":null,"ThankYouEmailMessage":null,"ValidateMessage":"false","ValidationMessageLibrary":null,"InactiveSurvey":"DefaultMessage","PartialDeletion":null,"PartialDataCloseAfter":"LastActivity","InactiveMessageLibrary":null,"InactiveMessage":null,"AvailableLanguages":{"EN":[]},"BallotBoxStuffingPreventionBehavior":"DefaultMessage","BallotBoxStuffingPreventionMessage":null,"BallotBoxStuffingPreventionMessageLibrary":null,"BallotBoxStuffingPreventionURL":null,"RecaptchaV3":"true","ConfirmStart":true,"AutoConfirmStart":true,"RelevantID":"false","RelevantIDLockoutPeriod":"+30 days","SurveyName":"Chatbot Identity E4 - After Revision"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"QGO","PrimaryAttribute":"QGO_QuotaGroupOrder","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":["QG_igbrgtQcMmjsH6c"]},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SCO","PrimaryAttribute":"Scoring","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ScoringCategories":[],"ScoringCategoryGroups":[],"ScoringSummaryCategory":null,"ScoringSummaryAfterQuestions":0,"ScoringSummaryAfterSurvey":0,"DefaultScoringCategory":null,"AutoScoringCategory":null}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"PROJ","PrimaryAttribute":"CORE","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":"1.1.0","Payload":{"ProjectCategory":"CORE","SchemaVersion":"1.1.0"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":false,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID94","SecondaryAttribute":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Educati.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<br>\n<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nNow, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Education Tutor.<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nTo start interacting with&nbsp;<strong>the AI Tutor<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>enter your Prolific Turk ID: <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">${q:\/\/QID105\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/span>&nbsp;on the interaction website<\/strong>. After entering your ID, you will be redirected to the interaction&nbsp;page.&nbsp;<strong>Once you finish the interaction, you will get a <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">completion code<\/span> that you need to copy and paste below.<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>Please continue filling out the rest of the form after you finish the interaction, if you do not finish the form after finishing the interaction, you will not receive payment.<\/strong><br><br>\nPlease open the link in a&nbsp;<strong>separate tab (do not close this tab).&nbsp;<\/strong>We recommend that you open it using<strong>&nbsp;Google Chrome.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/eillab.xyz\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here is a link to the website<\/a><br>\n<br>\nFor any issues, please email:&nbsp;<strong>[anonymized]<\/strong><br>\nEnjoy!","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"interaction_prompt","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Educati...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID94","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID184","SecondaryAttribute":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Educati.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<br \/>\n<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nNow, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Education Tutor.<br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nTo start interacting with&nbsp;<strong>the AI Tutor<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>enter your Mechanical Turk ID: <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">${q:\/\/QID105\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/span>&nbsp;on the interaction website<\/strong>. After entering your ID, you will be redirected to the interaction&nbsp;page.&nbsp;<strong>Once you finish the interaction, you will get a <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">completion code<\/span> that you need to copy and paste below.<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>Please continue filling out the rest of the form after you finish the interaction, if you do not finish the form after finishing the interaction, you will not receive payment.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nPlease open the link in a&nbsp;<strong>separate tab (do not close this tab).&nbsp;<\/strong>We recommend that you open it using<strong>&nbsp;Google Chrome.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/eillab.xyz\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here is a link to the website<\/a><br \/>\n<br \/>\nFor any issues, please email:&nbsp;<strong>[anonymized]<\/strong><br \/>\nEnjoy!","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"interac-2","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Educati...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID184","DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"LogicType":"Question","LeftOperand":"q:\/\/undefined\/undefined","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"Error\">Invalid Logic<\/span> <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" clickcallback=\"Qualtrics.DisplayLogic.edit:DL_55451190\" instanceid=\"LE_24707296\">Click Here to Edit Logic<\/a>"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID182","SecondaryAttribute":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to see a website explaining a..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<br>\n<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nNow, you will get a chance to see a website explaining a math principle.<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nTo access the website,&nbsp;<strong>enter your Mechanical Turk ID: <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">${q:\/\/QID105\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/span>&nbsp;on the website<\/strong>. After entering your ID, you will be redirected to the&nbsp; page.&nbsp;<strong>Once you finish reading the content in the website, you will get a <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">completion code<\/span> that you need to copy and paste below.<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>Please continue filling out the rest of the form after you finish reading the website, if you do not finish the form after finishing reading the website, you will not receive payment.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nPlease open the link in a&nbsp;<strong>separate tab (do not close this tab).&nbsp;<\/strong>We recommend that you open it using<strong>&nbsp;Google Chrome.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/eillab.xyz\">Here is a link to the website<\/a><br>\n<br>\nFor any issues, please email:&nbsp;<strong>[anonymized]<\/strong><br>\nEnjoy!","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will get a chance to see a website explaining a...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<br \/>\n<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nNow, you will get a chance to interact with an AI Education Tutor.<br \/>\n&nbsp;<br \/>\nTo start interacting with&nbsp;<strong>the AI Tutor<\/strong>,&nbsp;<strong>enter your Mechanical Turk ID: <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">${q:\/\/QID105\/ChoiceTextEntryValue}<\/span>&nbsp;on the interaction website<\/strong>. After entering your ID, you will be redirected to the interaction&nbsp;page.&nbsp;<strong>Once you finish the interaction, you will get a <span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">completion code<\/span> that you need to copy and paste below.<\/strong>&nbsp;<strong>Please continue filling out the rest of the form after you finish the interaction, if you do not finish the form after finishing the interaction, you will not receive payment.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nPlease open the link in a&nbsp;<strong>separate tab (do not close this tab).&nbsp;<\/strong>We recommend that you open it using<strong>&nbsp;Google Chrome.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/eillab.xyz\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here is a link to the website<\/a><br \/>\n<br \/>\nFor any issues, please email:&nbsp;<strong>[anonymized]<\/strong><br \/>\nEnjoy!","DataExportTag":"Q182","QuestionID":"QID182"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID136","SecondaryAttribute":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will use YouTube for 15 minutes. While using You.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nNow, you will use <strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">YouTube<\/span><\/strong> for 15 minutes. While using YouTube, you can do anything you want like watching videos, browsing comments, commenting on videos, etc.<br>\n<br>\nTo be able to verify that you used YouTube, we request a screenshot of your history for the last 15 minutes after you used YouTube. For this, make sure you are logged in to your YouTube account before using YouTube. Then, you should take a screenshot of your history for the last 15 minutes after visiting <a href=\"https:\/\/myactivity.google.com\/product\/youtube?hl=en&amp;utm_medium=mobile-web&amp;utm_source=youtube\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">this link<\/a>. Here is an example screenshot:<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/hbs.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_7TxZcnVonp96Iaq\" style=\"width: 1346px; height: 1484px;\"><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Please click the 'Start Timer' button below and start using&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">YouTube<\/a>&nbsp;for 15 minutes, in a separate tab. After you use YouTube for 15 minutes, you will be able to upload your screenshot.<br>\n<br>\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Note:<\/span> <\/strong>You will not receive payment if you fail to show evidence that you used YouTube. If your history does not fit in a single screenshot, you can send multiple screenshots.&nbsp;<strong>Please make sure you contain the \"today\" heading in the screenshot, as well as the names of the videos and the time they are watched. <\/strong>For questions, you can email [anonymized]<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div align=\"center\"><button class=\"btn btn-primary\" id=\"start_timer\" type=\"button\">Start Timer<\/button>\n<p id=\"safeTimerDisplay\"><strong>15:00<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"info","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will use YouTube for 15 minutes. While using You...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID136","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\t\t\t\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\/\/\t$('NextButton').hide();\n\tthis.hideNextButton();\n\n\tconst interval = 500;\n\tvar startTime;\n\tvar deadline;\n\n\tfunction step() {\n\t\tif((deadline - Date.now()) <= 0) {\n\t\t\t\/\/ Enable next question\n\t\t\t$('NextButton').show();\n\t\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = \"You can go to next question to upload your screenshot now\";\n\t\t\treturn(0);\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tvar distance = deadline - Date.now();\n\t\tvar minutes = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60 * 60)) \/ (1000 * 60));\n\t\tvar seconds = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60)) \/ 1000);\n\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = minutes + \":\" + seconds;\n\n\t\tvar expected = Date.now() + interval;\n\t\tvar drift = Date.now() - expected; \/\/ the drift (positive for overshooting)\n\t\tconsole.log(drift);\n\t\tconsole.log(expected);\n\n\t\texpected += interval;\n\t\tsetTimeout(step, Math.max(0, interval - drift)); \/\/ take into account drift\n\n\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\/\/ Event listeners for main thread\n\tdocument.getElementById(\"start_timer\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(){\n\t\tdocument.getElementById(\"start_timer\").style.display = 'none';\n\n\t\tstartTime = Date.now();\n\t\tdeadline = 15 * 60 * 1000 + startTime;\n\t\tsetTimeout(step(), interval);\n\t});\n\t\n\t$(window).focus(function() {\n\t\t\/\/ Check remaining time, if its <= 0, submit\n\t\tif((deadline - Date.now()) <= 0) {\n\t\t\t\/\/ Enable next question\n\t\t\t$('NextButton').show();\n\t\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = \"You can go to next question to upload your screenshot now\";\n\t\t}\n\t});\n\t\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\tclearInterval();\n\n});"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID173","SecondaryAttribute":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will\u00a0not interact with anything,\u00a0and will just ","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nNow, you will&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">not interact with anything,&nbsp;and will just be alone with your thoughts. In other words, you will not use any technological device and not interact with another person or pet&nbsp;<\/span><\/strong>for 15 minutes.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Please click the 'Start Timer' button below and <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">do not interact with anything, includ<\/span><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">ing your computer, your cellphone, or another person\/pet&nbsp;for 15 minutes.<\/span><\/strong><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Note:<\/strong> Please do not leave this page after you start the timer. You will be able to go to the next question after 15 minutes.<br>\n&nbsp;\n<div align=\"center\"><button type=\"button\" id=\"start_timer\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Start Timer<\/button>\n<p id=\"safeTimerDisplay\"><strong>15:00<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !\u00a0 \u00a0 Now, you will\u00a0not interact with anything,\u00a0and will just b...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page loads*\/\n\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function()\n{\t\t\t\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is fully displayed*\/\n\tthis.hideNextButton();\n\n\tconst interval = 500;\n\tvar startTime;\n\tvar deadline;\n\n\tfunction step() {\n\t\tif((deadline - Date.now()) <= 0) {\n\t\t\t\/\/ Enable next question\n\t\t\tconsole.log(\"Time finished\")\n\t\t\t$('NextButton').show();\n\t\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = \"You can go to next question now\";\n\t\t\treturn(0);\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tvar distance = deadline - Date.now();\n\t\tvar minutes = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60 * 60)) \/ (1000 * 60));\n\t\tvar seconds = Math.floor((distance % (1000 * 60)) \/ 1000);\n\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = minutes + \":\" + seconds;\n\n\t\tvar expected = Date.now() + interval;\n\t\tvar drift = Date.now() - expected; \/\/ the drift (positive for overshooting)\n\t\tconsole.log(drift);\n\t\tconsole.log(expected);\n\n\t\texpected += interval;\n\t\tsetTimeout(step, Math.max(0, interval - drift)); \/\/ take into account drift\n\n\t}\n\t\t\t\n\t\/\/ Event listeners for main thread\n\tdocument.getElementById(\"start_timer\").addEventListener(\"click\", function(){\n\t\tdocument.getElementById(\"start_timer\").style.display = 'none';\n\n\t\tstartTime = Date.now();\n\t\tdeadline = 15 * 60 * 1000 + startTime;\n\t\tsetTimeout(step(), interval);\n\t});\n\t\n\t$(window).focus(function() {\n\t\t\/\/ Check remaining time, if its <= 0, submit\n\t\tif((deadline - Date.now()) <= 0) {\n\t\t\t\/\/ Enable next question\n\t\t\t$('NextButton').show();\n\t\t\tdocument.querySelector('#safeTimerDisplay').textContent = \"You can go to next question to upload your screenshot now\";\n\t\t}\n\t});\n\t\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnUnload(function()\n{\n\t\/*Place your JavaScript here to run when the page is unloaded*\/\n\tclearInterval();\n\n});","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<strong>! THIS IS CRUCIAL FOR YOUR PAYMENT !&nbsp;<\/strong><br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nNow, you will use <strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">YouTube<\/span><\/strong> for 15 minutes. While using YouTube, you can do anything you want like watching videos, browsing comments, commenting on videos, etc.<br>\n<br>\nTo be able to verify that you used YouTube, we request a screenshot of your history for the last 15 minutes after you used YouTube. For this, make sure you are logged in to your YouTube account before using YouTube. Then, you should take a screenshot of your history for the last 15 minutes after visiting <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/myactivity.google.com\/product\/youtube?hl=en&amp;utm_medium=mobile-web&amp;utm_source=youtube\">this link<\/a>. Here is an example screenshot:<br>\n<br>\n<img style=\"width: 1346px; height: 1484px;\" src=\"https:\/\/hbs.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_7TxZcnVonp96Iaq\"><br>\n<br>\n<strong>Please click the 'Start Timer' button below and start using&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/\">YouTube<\/a>&nbsp;for 15 minutes, in a separate tab. After you use YouTube for 15 minutes, you will be able to upload your screenshot.<br>\n<br>\n<span style=\"color:#c0392b;\">Note:<\/span> <\/strong>You will not receive payment if you fail to show evidence that you used YouTube. If your history does not fit in a single screenshot, you can send multiple screenshots.&nbsp;<strong>Please make sure you contain the \"today\" heading in the screenshot, as well as the names of the videos and the time they are watched.<\/strong><br>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<button type=\"button\" id=\"start_timer\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Start Timer<\/button>\n\n<strong><p id=\"safeTimerDisplay\">15:00<\/p><\/strong>\n<\/div>","DataExportTag":"noInteraction","QuestionID":"QID173"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID89","SecondaryAttribute":"...less\/more comfortable.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"...less\/more&nbsp;comfortable.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"comfort_predict","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":10,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":true,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true,"SliderStartPositions":{"3":0.50066050198150591210577431411365978419780731201171875}},"QuestionDescription":"...less\/more comfortable.","Choices":{"3":{"Display":"&nbsp;"}},"ChoiceOrder":["3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":10,"NextAnswerId":3,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Definitely Less Comfortable<\/span>"},"2":{"Display":"<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Definitely More Comfortable<\/span>"}},"QuestionID":"QID89"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID100","SecondaryAttribute":"...less\/more comfortable.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"...less\/more comfortable.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":10,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":true,"NotApplicable":false,"Mo