s. This could range from engaging in daily conversation, providing emotional support, or even expressing romantic sentiments.&nbsp;<strong>${e:\/\/Field\/closeness_prompt}<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<br \/>\nAfter your interaction with this app of several months, the company updated the app. After this update,<strong>&nbsp;${e:\/\/Field\/change_prompt}<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"intro_3","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal AI companion app for 19,99$ per month. Th...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID215"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID203","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion app for 19,99$ per month. This AI companion is designed to provide companionship in both friendly and romantic contexts. This could range from engaging in daily conversation, providing emotional support, or even expressing romantic sentiments, e.g., romantic role play and 'sexting'. ${e:\/\/Field\/closeness_prompt}\n\nImagine that after you have been using the app for several months, the company updates the app. After this update, ${e:\/\/Field\/change_prompt}.\n\nConsidering this, please answer the questions in the following pages.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"intro","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID203","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID254","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion app for $19.99 per month. AI companions are capable of engaging with the user in both friendly and romantic contexts. This includes engaging in daily conversation, providing emotional support, and even expressing romantic sentiments, e.g., romantic role play, which the companion reciprocates.&nbsp;<strong>Imagine that you are in a meaningful relationship with your AI companion.<\/strong><\/span><br>\n<br>\nImagine that after you have been using the app for several months, the company updates the app. After this update,<strong>&nbsp;${e:\/\/Field\/change_prompt}. The company also enabled the users to have version history of the AI companion, i.e., it's now possible to revert to the AI companion before the update.<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nConsidering this, please answer the extent to which you agree with the statements that follow.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"intro_2","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID254","DisplayLogic":{"0":{"0":{"LogicType":"EmbeddedField","LeftOperand":"change_type","Operator":"EqualTo","RightOperand":"closeness_revert","Type":"Expression","Description":"<span class=\"ConjDesc\">If<\/span>  <span class=\"LeftOpDesc\">change_type<\/span> <span class=\"OpDesc\">Is Equal to<\/span> <span class=\"RightOpDesc\"> closeness_revert <\/span>"},"Type":"If"},"Type":"BooleanExpression","inPage":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID255","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<span style=\"color:#7f8c8d;\">Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion app for $19.99 per month. AI companions are capable of engaging with the user in both friendly and romantic contexts. This includes engaging in daily conversation, providing emotional support, and even expressing romantic sentiments, e.g., romantic role play, which the companion reciprocates. Imagine that you are in a meaningful relationship with your AI companion.<\/span><br>\n<br>\nImagine that after you have been using the app for several months, the company updates the app. After this update,<strong>&nbsp;${e:\/\/Field\/change_prompt}<\/strong>.<br>\n<br>Considering this, please answer the extent to which you agree with the statements that follow.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"intro_3","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID255"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID256","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine that you are a monthly subscriber to a personal, artificial intelligence (AI) companion a...","TertiaryAttrib