":"QID237"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID263","SecondaryAttribute":"In some sense, after the change, I would feel that the original AI companion was no longer around...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In some sense, after the change, I would feel that the original AI companion was no longer around any more.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":10,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":true,"SliderStartPositions":{"1":0.5},"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"In some sense, after the change, I would feel that the original AI companion was no longer around...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"&nbsp;"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":3,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"Strongly agree"}},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"In some sense, after the change, I would feel that the original AI companion was no longer around any more.","DataExportTag":"Q263","QuestionID":"QID263"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID62","SecondaryAttribute":"In this study, you will interact with AI math tutor\u00a0${e:\/\/Field\/condition} for\u00a015 minutes. Please.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this study, you will interact with AI math tutor&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">${e:\/\/Field\/condition}<\/span> <\/strong>for&nbsp;<strong>15 minutes<\/strong>. Please assume that you have a child 8 years old who is going to learn the division from this tutor. You can ask questions\/orient a tutor to teach your child about division in math. You can enter a prompt that you would like to a service from the AI math tutor.<br>\n<br>\nBefore you do, we would like you to answer some questions about how you <b>expect<\/b>&nbsp;your willingness to pay for this service&nbsp;<b>after<\/b> the interaction.&nbsp;","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"vign","QuestionID":"QID62","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this study, you will interact with AI math tutor\u00a0${e:\/\/Field\/condition} for\u00a015 minutes. Please...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID156","SecondaryAttribute":"In this study, you will not interact with the AI Math tutor and will just be alone with your own...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this study, <span style=\"color:#2980b9;\"><strong>you will not interact with the AI Math tutor and will just be alone with your own mathematical skills. In other words, you will not use any technological device\/calculator and not interact with another human<\/strong><\/span><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong>for&nbsp;<strong>15 minutes<\/strong>.<br>\n<br>\nBefore you do, we would like you to answer some questions about how you <b>expect<\/b> to feel <b>after<\/b> not interacting with anything during the mathematical .&nbsp;","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this study, you will not interact with the AI Math tutor and will just be alone with your own...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"In this study, you will interact with <strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9;\">${e:\/\/Field\/condition}<\/span> <\/strong>for&nbsp;<strong>15 minutes<\/strong>.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nBefore you do, we would like you to answer some questions about how you <b>expect<\/b> to feel <b>after<\/b> the interaction.&nbsp;","DataExportTag":"text_noint ","QuestionID":"QID156"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID197","SecondaryAttribute":"In total, how many months have you been in this relationship?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>In total, how many months have you been in this relationship?<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"rep_relation_mos","QuestionID":"QID197","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In total, how many months have you been in this relationship?","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","MinChars":"1","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"","Max":"","NumDecimals":""}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":5,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID293","SecondaryAttribute":"In total, how many months have you been in this relationship? Please enter the total number of mo...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>In total, how many <u>months<\/u> have you been in this relationship?<\/strong><br \/>\nPlease enter the total number of months only.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"months_rep","QuestionID":"QID293","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In total, how many months have you been in this relationship? Please enter the total number of mo...","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"ContentType","MinChars":"1","ContentType":"ValidNumber","ValidDateType":"DateWithFormat","ValidPhoneType":"ValidUSPhone","ValidZipType":"ValidUSZip","ValidNumber":{"Min":"0","Max":"","NumDecimals":""}}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"SearchSource":{"AllowFreeResponse":"false"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID19","SecondaryAttribute":"Informed Consent Participation is voluntary It is your choice whether or not to participate in th...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Informed Consent<br>\n<br>\nParticipation is voluntary<\/strong><br>\nIt is your choice whether or not to participate in this research. If you choose to participate, you may change your mind and leave the study at any time. Refusal to participate or stopping your participation will involve no penalty or loss of benefits to which you are otherwise entitled.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>What is the purpose of this research?<\/strong><br>\nThe purpose of this research is to examine human judgments. All data from this experiment are gathered for scientific purposes.&nbsp;These data may be published in scientific journals so that other researchers may have access to these data.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>How long will I take part in this research?<\/strong><br>\nYour participation will take approximately 6 minutes to complete.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>What can I expect if I take part in this research?<\/strong><br role=\"presentation\">\nAs a participant, you will be asked several questions about AI companions.&nbsp;You will also be asked to complete a demographics form at the end.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>What are the risks and possible discomforts?<\/strong><br>\nIf you choose to participate, the effects should be comparable to those you would experience from viewing a computer monitor for 6 minutes and using a mouse or keyboard, e.g., eye fatigue. You are free to take breaks throughout the session.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>Will I be compensated for participating in this research?<\/strong><br>\nYou will be compensated $1.2 for this study.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<strong>If I take part in this research, how will my privacy be protected? What happens to the information you collect?<\/strong><br>\nYour participation in this experiment will remain confidential, and your identity will not be stored with your data.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>If I have any questions, concerns or complaints about this research study, who can I talk to?<\/strong><br>\nThe researcher for this study is [anonymized] who can be reached at 626.559.6401; [anonymized]. If you have questions, concerns, or complaints,<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you would like to talk to the research team,<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you think the research has harmed you, or<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you wish to withdraw from the study.<br>\n<br>\nThis research has been reviewed by the Committee on the Use of Human Subjects in Research at Harvard University. They can be reached at 617-496-2847, 1350 Massachusetts Avenue, Suite 935, Cambridge, MA 02138, or cuhs@harvard.edu for any of the following:<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If your questions, concerns, or complaints are not being answered by the research team,<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you cannot reach the research team,<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you want to talk to someone besides the research team, or<br role=\"presentation\">\n\u2022 If you have questions about your rights as a research participant.<\/p>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"consent","QuestionID":"QID19","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAHR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","LabelPosition":"BELOW"},"QuestionDescription":"Informed Consent Participation is voluntary It is your choice whether or not to participate in th...","Choices":{"8":{"Display":"I agree to participate in this study"},"9":{"Display":"I do NOT agree to participate in this study"}},"ChoiceOrder":["8","9"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":11,"NextAnswerId":1,"RecodeValues":{"8":"1","9":"2"}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID229","SecondaryAttribute":"Instructions:\u00a0The following questions ask about how you felt\u00a0DURING\u00a0the software update (the \"cha","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" \/><b>Instructions:&nbsp;<\/b>The following questions ask about how you felt&nbsp;<u>DURING<\/u>&nbsp;the software update (the &quot;change&quot;) that removed the erotic role play (ERP) feature. Please rate how often you felt the following.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"info","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Instructions:\u00a0The following questions ask about how you felt\u00a0DURING\u00a0the software update (the \"cha...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID229"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_5AnNYagjHZGw4oS","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID265","SecondaryAttribute":"Interacting with my AI companion makes me feel less lonely.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Interacting with my AI companion makes me feel less lonely.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":10,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":true,"SliderStartPositions":{"1":0.5},"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Interac